<body>
    {{>nav}}
    <div class="intro">
        <h1>Adobe Podcast AI Overview</h1>
        <div class="read-word"></div>
        <div class="count-word"></div>
        <p>Adobe Podcast AI is a brand-new AI-powered product that was just released for podcast producers by Adobe.
            The application is made to assist podcast producers in optimising their programmes and enhancing listener
            satisfaction.
        </p>
        <p>Advanced machine learning techniques are used by Adobe Podcast AI to assess audio content and offer
            suggestions for
            improving and editing it.
            The tool can identify problems including background noise, clipping, and low levels and provide solutions.
            Additionally, it includes recommendations for enhancing the podcast's overall production quality by using
            music, sound
            effects, and other audio components.
        </p>
        <p>One of Adobe Podcast AI's primary benefits is its capacity to instantly translate audio files, which makes it
            simpler
            for podcast producers to modify their programmes.
            The programme creates precise transcriptions through the use of speech recognition and natural language
            processing,
            which may subsequently be modified and improved upon as necessary.
        </p>
        <p>Adobe Podcast AI offers statistics and insights into the performance of a podcast in addition to editing and
            augmenting
            audio material.
            The most popular episodes, average listen time, and the total number of downloads are all available to
            creators.
            Making data-driven decisions based on this information can enable podcast makers to better engage their
            listeners and
            increase the overall success of their show.</p>
        <p>Another important feature of Adobe Podcast AI is its integration with the Adobe Creative Cloud. Podcast
            creators can
            easily access the tool from within Adobe Audition and other Creative Cloud applications, streamlining the
            production
            process and making it easier to create high-quality podcasts.</p>
        <p>In conclusion, Adobe Podcast AI is an effective tool for podcast producers that want to raise the level of
            production on
            their programmes and engage their listeners.
            The podcasting business is about to undergo a transformation as a result of Adobe Podcast AI's cutting-edge
            machine
            learning algorithms, real-time transcribing capabilities, and extensive analytics and insights.</p>

    </div>
    <script>
        const paragraphs = document.querySelectorAll(".intro p");
        const readTimeDiv = document.querySelector(".read-word");
        const count = document.querySelector(".count-word");

        const calculatedReadTime = ()=>{
            let numberOfWords = 0;
            const averageWPM = 265;

            paragraphs.forEach(paragraph =>{
                numberOfWords += paragraph.innerHTML.split(" ").length;
            })

            let readTime = numberOfWords / averageWPM;

            readTimeDiv.innerHTML = Math.round(readTime) + " minute read"
            count.innerHTML = numberOfWords + " -words approximate"

            {{!-- console.log("number of words"+numberOfWords) --}}
            {{!-- console.log("read time is " + Math.round(readTime)); --}}
        }
        calculatedReadTime();



    </script>

